short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Instantly change the browsing mode of your LinkedIn profile.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This chrome extension supports to change the browsing mode in LinkedIn with a single click.
It has three options:
1. The User's Name and headline
2. Private profile characteristics (i.e. Job Title and Industry)
3. Private Mode
And your changes will be saved in the Profile viewing options automatically.
